      <title>Tracking Hurricane Milton's destruction. And, why more Black men are backing the GOP</title>
      <author>Brittney Melton</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/10/10/g-s1-27395/up-first-newsletter-hurricane-milton-destruction-black-male-voters</link>
