      <title>Fact-checking the Vance-Walz debate. And, Biden to assess N.C. after Hurricane Helene</title>
      <author>Brittney Melton</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/10/02/g-s1-25901/up-first-newsletter-jd-vance-tim-walz-vice-presidential-debate-president-biden-north-carolina-hurricane-helene</link>
